---
layout: page.njk
title: "Members Directory - HIT Startup Club"
activePage: members
permalink: "members.html"
---
<main class="flex flex-col w-full pt-16 min-h-screen pb-20">
<section class="relative w-full py-20 lg:py-28 flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-background-light">
<div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-mesh z-0 pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-text-main mb-4">
                Members
            </h1>
<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-text-sub font-jp font-medium">
                個性豊かな才能が、未来を共創する。
            </p>
<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-sub/80 max-w-lg mx-auto font-jp">
                HIT Startup Clubには、エンジニア、デザイナー、マーケターなど、
                多様な専門性を持った学生が集まっています。
            </p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="sticky top-16 z-40 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-gray-100 py-4 mb-8">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2 md:gap-4 overflow-x-auto no-scrollbar pb-1">
<button class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-text-main text-white text-sm font-bold shadow-md transition-transform hover:scale-105 whitespace-nowrap">
                    All Members
                </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-text-sub hover:text-primary hover:border-primary text-sm font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                    Business
                </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-text-sub hover:text-primary hover:border-primary text-sm font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                    Technology
                </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-text-sub hover:text-primary hover:border-primary text-sm font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                    Design
                </button>
<button class="px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 text-text-sub hover:text-primary hover:border-primary text-sm font-medium transition-all hover:shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
                    Marketing
                </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mb-20">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8">
{% for member in collections.members %}
<a href="members/{{ member.data.slug }}.html" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col items-center text-center h-full" style="text-decoration:none;color:inherit;" data-category="{{ member.data.category }}">
<div class="relative w-28 h-28 mb-5">
<div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-cyan-accent opacity-20 blur-sm group-hover:opacity-40 transition-opacity"></div>
<div class="relative w-full h-full rounded-full overflow-hidden border-[3px] border-white shadow-inner">
<img alt="{{ member.data.nameEn }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="{{ member.data.photo }}"{% if member.data.photoStyle %} style="{{ member.data.photoStyle }}"{% endif %}/>
</div>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 font-jp mb-1">{{ member.data.name }}</h3>
<span class="text-sm font-bold text-gradient mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider text-[11px]">{{ member.data.role }}</span>
<p class="text-sm text-text-sub/80 font-jp mb-3 leading-relaxed line-clamp-3">
                    {{ member.data.summary }}
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-x-3 mb-5 font-jp">
{% for tag in member.data.tags %}<span class="text-xs text-gray-400">{{ tag }}</span>
{% endfor %}</div>
<div class="mt-auto flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
{% for badge in member.data.skillBadges %}<span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-wide rounded-md">{{ badge }}</span>
{% endfor %}</div>
</a>
{% endfor %}
</div>
</section>
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
<div class="relative rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-text-main text-white p-8 md:p-12 lg:p-16 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] -mr-20 -mt-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-80 h-80 bg-cyan-accent/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] -ml-20 -mb-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-white/10 border border-white/20 text-xs font-medium text-white mb-4">
<span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-primary animate-pulse"></span>
                    We are hiring
                </div>
<h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold font-jp mb-4">メンバー募集中</h2>
<p class="text-gray-300 font-jp max-w-xl text-lg">
                    私たちと一緒に、世界を変えるプロダクトを作りませんか？<br class="hidden md:block"/>
                    エンジニア、デザイナー、ビジネス職、全方位で募集中です。
                </p>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full md:w-auto">
<a href="https://line.me/ti/g2/I4hPOfn28NLrMfHr6Uln_BRtiXHN4ewwg5sbPw?utm_source=invitation&utm_medium=link_copy&utm_campaign=default" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-gradient h-14 px-8 rounded-full text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2 shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary/50 transition-all whitespace-nowrap" style="text-decoration:none;">
<span>Apply Now (応募する)</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
